    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for a Class II device with medium model influence. CFD predictions demonstrate mean relative error of 8.3% against FDA experimental data, within the 15% acceptance threshold. All operating conditions satisfy the RH < 1 criterion. The model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions in support of the CPB device submission.",
